Title: JET Range FVC thermostatic fire valve 95C 10mm x 3mtr
Description: Jet FVC Fuelstop safety fire valve designed to shut down the flow of fuel to the appliance in the event of the burner overheating or a fire near the appliance. The valve is to be installed in the oil line at point of entry to the building. The sensor to be passed though the wall into the building and positioned above the burner in accordance with the burner manufacturer's instructions. The oil line and capillary should be sleeved as it passes through walls and there should not be any sharp bends made in the capillary tube. The safety valve is of a robust mechanical design manufactured of non-corrosive materials for external installation. Please ensure that the valve is installed with the reset button pointing down so that rain water cannot enter the valve body. The reset button can be used as an isolation valve when the burner is being serviced by pulling the button down but must be pressed up to activate the valve into the open position before the burner is fired up.
